{"type": "article", "id": 52651, "title": "Nendo新设计的百叶窗，有自动打开的花朵｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-04-27T23:04:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 48772, "name": "Moebe"}, {"id": 49771, "name": "Micro Technology"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 29871, "name": "Blå Station"}, {"id": 49772, "name": "Diabla"}, {"id": 31678, "name": "Pedro Paulo Venzon"}, {"id": 49773, "name": "Mikiya Kobayashi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 175, "image": "img/article/article_show/2018042807034864EWUGVYMRtz5QSf.JPG", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Donut Stool by Mikiya Kobayashi for Diabla</h3><p>日本设计师 Mikiya Kobayashi 推出了一款甜甜圈凳子，简单却有吸引力。这是户外家具品牌 Diabla 委托设计师创作的，座垫部分是甜甜圈的形状，由一圈软泡沫制成，同时适合室内、室外空间，期待为当下流行的黑白灰空间带去一些乐趣和色彩，提供红色、粉红色和芥末色三种选择。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215724Ac70foVaLdlIpegh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215724qokCUc4Z3QwetgrO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215724gUPsN5euOc3pYEt4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215725CoIcatvw3pq1K4g6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804272157259V10p82SvCOjalIQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215725RLPAZy3kEbFvmCpt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.designboom.com/design/mikiya-kobayashi-donut-stool-diabla-04-27-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Designboom</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Bob Sofa System by Stefan Borselius and Thomas Bernstrand</h3><p>最近，瑞典家具制造商 Blå Station 邀请设计师 Stefan Borselius 和 Thomas Bernstrand，设计了 Bob 沙发系统，小型模块的设计便于每一部分轻松融入到任何组合配置中。</p><p>按照设计师的说法，Bob 沙发系统是将斯堪的纳维亚风格和现代主义美学融合的一次尝试，适用于包括客厅、书房、公共空间以及办公空间等不同氛围的场所。7 种类型模块的选择，也容易搭配出更多个性化组合方式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804272158201QEZrvamzPBp4We8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.495312\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215820Fj3OD2xdMekIsNq7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.470313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215820wtgejqGakFENXICB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.503125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215820SFrGmIUy1LgQvYte.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.775000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804272158211kCzbjW0fl9BXHxF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215821UKsvxcX8DP1j45Am.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.823438\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/bla-station-will-keep-you-comfortable-and-connected-in-the-office/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Blooming Shades by Nendo for Micro Technology</h3><p>日本设计工作室 Nendo 提出了一种百叶窗的创新解决方案，以一种轻柔的方式覆盖窗户，挑战对“阻挡”窗口的普遍认知，是为日本公司 Micro Technology 量身而做的新品。</p><p>Blooming Shades 利用开放和闭合状态之间的转换作为设计的切入点，并对人们的运动和光线的强度做出反应。百叶窗上的花瓣图形会像盛开的花朵一样移动。它由两层高质量的遮光膜组成，夹在中间的是一层形状记忆合金。</p><p>通电时形状记忆合金就会产生电阻并产生热量，将薄膜推向外，从而勾勒出花的形状。当阳光变得更强或房间内的温度上升时，花朵就会自动打开以遮挡明亮的光线，保持舒适的室温。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=j0639ht8ka7&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215950aG7WSFpcI4hQYlMO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018042721595153AIwchz2orj6f7x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215951cYLdKq2TV9RxEFiz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804272159529cDr6XRIAKhayBd2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427215953cB9WrxyTaRZQX5q3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804272159548SUXbTsOL2QxnF5P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/blooming-shades/?erelease\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nendo</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Coat Rack by Moebe</h3><p>哥本哈根设计工作室 Moebe 推出一款新品衣架，它的金属杆上可穿入 4 到 6 个挂钩。</p><p>这些挂钩可沿金属杆灵活移动，为不同风格的衣物找到悬挂的最佳姿势。此外，该金属杆还可以从墙面随意拆解，方便挂钩的灵活处置。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220208zL78dn1fwuhBrYbv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751190\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220208XPDfShHlts013jRd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.520238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220208ueWIQqrNMUangDA1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.511905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804272202095f78iTqYted4nCby.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.803125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804272202090uiJQX3q8rzBaYdn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.497619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220209cRTaL0tkx19ySPKJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.565476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.moebe.dk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Moebe</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Profana by Pedro Paulo Venzon</h3><p>意大利哲学家 Giorgio Agamben 曾说，世俗化即是将人类领域带往原本只属于神的领域。设计师 Pedro Paulo Venzon 受到这句话的启发，设计了 Profana 系列灯具，背后的思考有关于拉丁美洲的建筑美学以及宗教融合主义，强调的是当今文化正处于剧烈转型期的事实。</p><p>这个系列试图唤起人们对于人造事物的关联性及重复性的审视，体现在灯杆与建筑空间之间，也体现在圆环与灯具的结构之间。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220256wmTD8pXCNMQY7be9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804272202567SRJuf840nEB3oaW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220256Wl5rjI6sL7KxeEi1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220257Swk2oN5ZYqWGfC9U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220256IzeHLsX4qcGFpO3g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.429231\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.pedrovenzon.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pedro Paulo Venzon</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>KI ECOBE by KI</h3><p>KI ECOBE 是一款新概念环保鞋，将拖鞋、普通鞋与凉鞋的功能结合在一款鞋里。它可以通过使用模块化零件的组装与拆解来实现三双不同种类的鞋子。每个组成部分都有着不同的作用，因此你可以毫不费力地就能够在家中、户外甚至是沙滩上实现鞋子的转换。</p><p>KI ECOBE 使用了无毒材料，因此经过简单的组装与拆解之后，还能实现产品的回收再利用，必要的时候可以使用替代组件。由于该产品独特的组装式设计，KI ecobe还具有高度的可定制化特点。用户可以下载 APP 后为鞋子的每个部分挑选颜色以及材料。目前，这款鞋正在 Kickstarter上众筹，早鸟价 79 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1121278858/ki-ecobe-customizable-self-assembled-footwear?\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220426XAhmbiz98q5nDGwM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220427ixPcfqXsuzDZgEyw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220427qH532oWmc9UVxpeI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220426ITkuNq5rimZ0VCLd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220427FtHhrMX3kd60E7qL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220428GML0FrS8ROzEvm7e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.808571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180427220430ZuMWq2CUaNRIfyGT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}